<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='304101' id='t-304101'>Why not try to give them some type
of insight to make a change,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='308322' id='t-308322'>so once they reenter back into society,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='311783' id='t-311783'>they're doing something positive?</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 5:27
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='316217' id='t-316217'>A second big thing to help our teens
in jails is better programming.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='321626' id='t-321626'>When I was on Rikers Island,
the huge thing was solitary confinement.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='325644' id='t-325644'>Solitary confinement
