<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='328373' id='t-328373'>to break a person mentally,
physically and emotionally.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='332065' id='t-332065'>That's what it was designed for.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='335756' id='t-335756'>The U.S. Attorney General
recently released a report</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='338224' id='t-338224'>stating that they're going
