<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='340749' id='t-340749'>in New York state for teens.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 5:54
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='343698' id='t-343698'>One thing that kept me sane while I
was in solitary confinement was reading.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='347900' id='t-347900'>I tried to educate myself
as much as possible.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='350802' id='t-350802'>I read any and everything
