<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='375139' id='t-375139'>how to write and make music?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='377536' id='t-377536'>Just a thought.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:29
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='378960' id='t-378960'>When adolescents come to Rikers Island,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='381029' id='t-381029'>C74, RNDC is the building
