<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='385143' id='t-385143'>That's nicknamed &quot;gladiator school,&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='388704' id='t-388704'>because you have a young individual
coming in from the street</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='391586' id='t-391586'>thinking that they're tough,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='393363' id='t-393363'>being surrounded by a bunch
of other young individuals</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='396683' id='t-396683'>from all of the five boroughs,
and everybody feels that they're tough.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='400327' id='t-400327'>So now you have a bunch of young gentlemen
poking their chests out</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='404322' id='t-404322'>feeling that I have to prove
I'm equally as tough as you</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='407712' id='t-407712'>or I'm tougher than you, you and you.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='410146' id='t-410146'>But let's be honest:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='411734' id='t-411734'>That culture is very dangerous
