</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:17
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='426311' id='t-426311'>It's sad to report
that while I was in prison,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='429762' id='t-429762'>I used to hear dudes talking about
