<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='481568' id='t-481568'>But I will tell you this:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='483424' id='t-483424'>Being in jail and being in prison,</span>
