 8:57
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='526081' id='t-526081'>So I walk up to him and I said,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='527895' id='t-527895'>&quot;O.G., what's going on, man, you good?&quot;</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:00
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='529857' id='t-529857'>He looked at me, and he said,
